Package: ffmpeg
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper for 'ffmpeg' Video Software
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sean", "Kross", email = "sean@seankross.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("John", "Muschelli", email = "muschellij2@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Creates wrapper functions for the 'ffmpeg' <https://ffmpeg.org/>
    software to allow users to create videos from images and splice in
    other video inputs.
SystemRequirements: ffmpeg (>= 3.2.4)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
